      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It has significant mechanical issues that will require immediate attention, and the exterior shows heavy wear, including dents and paint fading. The interior also requires a deep cleaning and some repairs. This would be a suitable project for a mechanic or someone looking for a low-cost parts car.",
