      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of the highest caliber. This vehicle remains in an uncompromising state, reflecting a standard of preservation rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. Every surface and mechanical component adheres to factory-original standards, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine asset, meticulously maintained for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
